      {
        "id" : "a0d49348-242b-4e67-a12d-3573ae40e00b",
        "parentId" : null,
        "authorId" : "a3f1fdb0-47ad-411e-b63d-af6fc71a1fa6",
        "body" : "Since this is header only and we need the compilers to pass some checks, this will have `run_exports` of the compilers applied. Meaning the compiler runtime libraries will be added. However we don't need those. So we can add `ignore_run_exports` here to avoid them from being added. Would suggest adding the following.\r\n\r\n```yaml\r\n  ignore_run_exports:\r\n    - libcxx\r\n    - libgcc-ng\r\n    - libstdcxx-ng\r\n    - vc\r\n    - vs2015_runtime\r\n```",
        "createdAt" : "2018-08-10T13:56:31Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2018-08-10T14:38:32Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "a3f1fdb0-47ad-411e-b63d-af6fc71a1fa6",
        "tags" : [
        ]
